==English==

===Noun===
'''bora'''
# A cold, often dry, [[northeas]]terly [[wind]] which blows, sometimes in violent gusts, down from
mountains on the eastern shore of the [[Adriatic]]. It also applies to cold, squally, downslope winds in other
parts of the world.

